Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是来挖墓的 到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头被切下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被防腐处理过了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是胸口被刺而死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过防腐处理后才被割下头颅的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有头部腐烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去问一下管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意思犯人就是墓地的管理人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是叫你去问 到底是谁搬来了这具尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无阿弥陀佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是东洋的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是祈祷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那具尸体 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是穿着整齐的官员们搬来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是 我要回剧院了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出就快要开始了
